title: The Jazz Butcher - Girl Go, Best Of Creation Years 87-98 (FLAC)
description:
The Jazz Butcher - Girl Go, The Best Of The Creation Years 1987-1998, 2-CD Set!


This is a best of I compiled myself. All tracks were ripped from CD in fabulous FLAC. I did not want to monkey around with changing the track numbers lest I screw things up. So each CD is in its own file & I have included a Text Document with the track order for each disk. 

I wanted to share this terrific music with new listeners & old. I hope you enjoy it as much as I do!
